OL,3,CFormer police officer stole #2.50 from
OL,4,Csuspect's car to pay for tuck shop debt
OL,6,FA former Thames Valley Police officer
OL,7,Fwho stole #2.50 from a suspect's car
OL,8,Fhas been told he would have been
OL,9,Fsacked if he hadn't already quit.
OL,11,FA disciplinary hearing was told PC
OL,12,FJames Tillcock took the money to pay
OL,13,Foff a debt at the tuck shop of his
OL,14,Fstation in Bicester.
OL,16,FOn 21st June, Tillcock was on duty
OL,17,Fwhen he searched a car in Kidlington
OL,18,Fafter the driver had been arrested.
