OL,3,CFormer police officer stole #2.50 from
OL,4,Csuspect's car to pay for tuck shop debt
OL,6,FJason Hogg, Chief Constable, Thames
OL,7,FValley Police said: "Although the
OL,8,Famount of money stolen was very low,
OL,9,Fthe behaviour shows a propensity for
OL,10,Fdishonesty and the fact that the
OL,11,Fformer Police Constable Tillcock is
OL,12,Funable to meet the high professional
OL,13,Fstandards expected of all police
OL,14,Fofficers and staff.
OL,16,F"The sanction is necessary to protect
OL,17,Fpublic confidence in the Police
OL,18,FService, making it clear that improper
OL,19,Fbehaviour will not be tolerated."
